    Assessment: Position appears deliberate
    rather than accidental

    Hypothesis: Object may serve as environmental marker
    rather than utility device

    Anomaly Flag: Purpose ambiguity increasing'
  - 'Object: Suspended Target System.

    Observed State: Resting where it was last
